data.description: ***OPEN HOUSE 2/4 CANCELED***  Step into this inviting 1136 SqFt Ranch nestled in Macomb with Utica schools. Immerse yourself in a move-in-ready haven renovated in 2008, eagerly awaiting your personal flair. This is an entertainer's paradise—bask in the natural light of the living room with crown molding and hardwood floors. The expansive eat-in kitchen with ceramic flooring, ample cabinet space, granite countertops, wainscoting walls, and a charming tile backsplash. A half bath adorns this culinary haven. Discover generously sized bedrooms adjacent to a well-appointed main bath. The finished basement unveils additional entertainment space and a kitchen equipped with a sink, dishwasher, refrigerator, and elevated countertops. Extend your gatherings outdoors onto the delightful deck, enveloped by a fully fenced yard. Note: Exclusions from the sale include the hot tub, ring doorbell, security cameras, and wood racks in the laundry room. Tear off roof with transferable warranty 7/22, water tank less than 5 years old, gutters 7/22. Welcome home to your refined retreat.
